dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Adams County, WI 2016
dc_description_s: This data layer represents hydrography for Adams County, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Adams_Hydro_2016.gdb.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current version of this data please visit: https://adams-county-open-data-portal-adams-county-wi.hub.arcgis.com/
